# Ament Law Group, P.C.

> Ament Law Group, P.C. is a law firm in Murrysville, Pennsylvania serving six counties in Western Pennsylvania. The firm focuses on estate planning, probate and trust administration, real estate settlement services, business law, and elder law.

## About the Firm

Ament Law Group, P.C. is a 12-person law firm located at 3950 Wm Penn Highway, Suite 5, Murrysville, PA 15668. The firm was co-founded by W. Robert Ament and John W. Ament. The attorneys at the firm are licensed to practice in Pennsylvania state courts and the U.S. District Court for the Western District of Pennsylvania. The firm serves clients across Westmoreland, Allegheny, Washington, Butler, Fayette, and Indiana Counties.

